<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="Aink354">
<l>īrmpiṇavu puṇarnta cennā yēṟṟai</l>
<l>maṟiyuṭai māṉpiṇai koḷḷātu kaḻiyu</l>
<l>mariya curaṉvan taṉarē</l>
<l>teriyiḻai yarivainiṉ paṇputara viraintē</l>
      </lg>
     <lg type="translation" xml:lang="en">
<l>O woman with choice jewels! </l>
<l>Hasting to obtain your goodness, </l>
<l>he returned from the harsh desert, </l>
<l>where a male jackal that mated with his loving female, </l>
<l>passed by without taking [the life] of a female deer with her fawn. </l>
      </lg>
    </div>
